articles.title: Israel-Hamas truce extended by 2 days, says Qatar - Financial Times
articles.description: Deal intended to allow more captives held in Gaza to be freed
articles.content:
Qatar said on Monday mediators had secured a deal to prolong the temporary truce between Israel and Hamas by two days to allow the release of more hostages held in Gaza.
